Package: lessedit
Architecture: amd_64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Markdown editor/viewer that exports to PDF and HTML.
 .
 A WYSIWYG Markdown editor based on the Sundown parser and WebKit. 
 Simple tabbed view interface with both WYSIWYG and HTML output.
 Also supports SmartyPants and inline HTML. Can export to PDF and HTML.
 Conveniently acts as a reader in view-mode.
